258
0:14:26.94,000 --> 0:14:28,000
This is what they're doing for our young people.

259
0:14:29.5,000 --> 0:14:32,000
Why are these groups doing this for our young people and not us?

260
0:14:34.58,000 --> 0:14:35,000
The thing is,

261
0:14:36.18,000 --> 0:14:39,000
I'm not trying to justify

262
0:14:39.54,000 --> 0:14:42,000
