275
0:15:23.9,000 --> 0:15:24,000
by becoming violent themselves.

276
0:15:25.42,000 --> 0:15:3,000
In fact, I found something, to my horror, that I recognized.

277
0:15:30.74,000 --> 0:15:36,000
